(13, 'Flux Festival 2025: Oslo‚Äôs Underground Trance & Techno Haven Returns', 'From hypnotic trance to pounding techno, Flux Festival 2025 is set to turn Hausmania into Oslo‚Äôs ultimate rave sanctuary this spring.', 'Flux Festival 2025 is making its much-anticipated return to Hausmania, Oslo, promising a two-day deep dive into the city‚Äôs underground sound culture. Scheduled for March 14‚Äì15, the event will spotlight both established and emerging talents from Norway‚Äôs thriving electronic scene.<br>\n\n<p>Leading the charge are local heavy-hitters Ekkel and SLYM, known for their marathon DJ sets and ability to shift seamlessly between hypnotic trance and driving techno. Expect intimate dance floors, low-lit visuals, and a crowd that‚Äôs there purely for the music.</p><br>\n\n<p>Flux has earned its reputation for community-driven curation, prioritizing raw energy and authenticity over commercial spectacle. The 2025 edition will feature a dual-stage setup ‚Äî one dedicated to deep, melodic trance, and the other to relentless, high-BPM techno ‚Äî giving attendees the freedom to drift between euphoric and intense moods.</p><br>\n\n<p>Hausmania‚Äôs warehouse aesthetic, paired with custom lighting rigs and immersive art, will provide the perfect backdrop for a 48-hour celebration of sound. With capacity limited, the festival is expected to sell out quickly.</p>', 5, 7, 'http://13.60.95.22:3001/uploads/images/articles/optimized-article-1755243505307-37841530.jpg', NULL, 'image', 1, 0, 1, 'published', 'Flux Festival 2025, Oslo Events, Hausmania, Trance Festival, Techno Festival, Underground Music, Norway Rave Scene, Ekkel, SLYM, European Festivals', 'Flux Festival 2025', 'Flux Festival 2025 returns to Oslo‚Äôs Hausmania with trance, techno, and Norway‚Äôs top underground DJs including Ekkel and SLYM.', 7, '2025-08-15 10:07:02', '2025-08-15 07:41:34', '2025-08-19 18:52:13'),
(14, 'Maiden Voyage Festival 2025: London‚Äôs Premier Day of House & Techno', 'Four stages, world-class DJs, and a full day of cutting-edge electronic music ‚Äî Maiden Voyage Festival 2025 is set to transform Burgess Park this August.', 'Maiden Voyage Festival returns to Burgess Park, London, on August 9, 2025, promising one of the UK capital‚Äôs most ambitious one-day electronic music lineups. This year‚Äôs roster reads like a love letter to the underground: Ben Klock, Blawan, and VTSS headline, supported by a deep selection of house, techno, and club innovators from across Europe.<br>\n\n<p>The festival will feature four distinct stages, each curated to showcase different sonic identities ‚Äî from relentless warehouse techno to groove-laden house sets and experimental club sounds. The main stage will see Ben Klock deliver his signature Berghain-honed techno, Blawan push the boundaries of industrial rhythms, and VTSS bring her high-octane blend of techno and rave energy.</p><br>\n\n<p>Beyond the music, Maiden Voyage prides itself on fostering an inclusive, community-focused atmosphere, drawing a diverse crowd of London‚Äôs ravers. Burgess Park‚Äôs central location offers easy access, making it the perfect spot for a summer day of dancing under open skies.<p/>', 5, 7, 'http://13.60.95.22:3001/uploads/images/articles/optimized-article-1755244520383-283902982.jpg', NULL, 'image', 1, 0, 0, 'published', 'Maiden Voyage Festival 2025, London Festivals, Burgess Park Events, UK House Scene, UK Techno Scene, Ben Klock, Blawan, VTSS, Summer Festivals UK', 'Maiden Voyage Festival 2025', 'Maiden Voyage Festival 2025 hits Burgess Park on August 9 with Ben Klock, Blawan, and VTSS across four stages of house, techno, and club sounds.', 5, '2025-08-15 10:05:36', '2025-08-15 07:54:22', '2025-08-16 16:03:09'),
(15, 'Peggy Gou Announces New Album ‚ÄúCity Lights‚Äù Inspired by Seoul‚Äôs Underground Scene', 'Peggy Gou is back with City Lights, a deep house and breakbeat fusion inspired by the sights and sounds of Seoul. The September 2025 release promises her most personal music yet.', '<p><strong>Peggy Gou</strong> has officially revealed details of her long-awaited album, <strong>City Lights</strong>, dropping September 2025. Recorded between Berlin and her hometown of Seoul, the record blends hypnotic deep house, 90s-inspired breakbeats, and Korean vocal samples collected from street performers in Itaewon.</p><br>\n\n<p>In an exclusive clip posted to Instagram, Peggy shared: ‚ÄúThis album is my love letter to Seoul ‚Äî the smells, the chaos, the people dancing until sunrise.‚Äù Fans quickly flooded the comments, calling it her ‚Äúmost personal work yet.‚Äù</p><br>\n\n<p>The first single, Neon Rain, is already climbing Beatport‚Äôs Deep House chart, with DJs praising its ‚Äúfloor-filling groove and cinematic drops.‚Äù Rumors are swirling about an intimate album launch party at a secret rooftop venue in Seoul, livestreamed globally.</p>', 1, 7, 'http://13.60.95.22:3001/uploads/images/articles/optimized-article-1755245905036-459820471.jpg', NULL, 'image', 0, 1, 0, 'published', 'Peggy Gou, City Lights Album, Deep House, Breakbeats, Korean Electronic Music, 2025 Music Releases, Seoul Club Scene', 'Peggy Gou‚Äôs ‚ÄúCity Lights‚Äù Album', 'Peggy Gou returns with City Lights, a deep house and breakbeat album inspired by Seoul‚Äôs underground culture.', 6, '2025-08-15 10:03:45', '2025-08-15 08:21:10', '2025-08-22 14:37:17'),
(16, 'Trance Revival Sweeps Europe in 2025', 'Trance is back! DJs across Europe are bringing euphoric 140 BPM sets to major festivals and clubs this year.', 'After years of underground cult followings, trance music is making a massive comeback across Europe in 2025. From Berlin warehouse parties to Ibiza beach stages, DJs are dropping euphoric 140 BPM sets, blending classic melodies with modern production techniques.<br>\n\nKey figures in the revival include Aly & Fila, Paul van Dyk, and rising talent Euphoric Soul, who are headlining festival stages and curated club nights. Social media trends show fans sharing festival clips and TikTok challenges set to the genre, fueling the resurgence.<br>\n\nIndustry insiders attribute this revival to a combination of nostalgia for early 2000s trance, the influence of electronic music platforms, and a renewed interest in high-energy melodic sets that keep dancers moving for hours. Festivals like Tomorrowland, A State of Trance Weekender, and Luminosity Beach Festival are embracing the trend, dedicating prime slots to trance acts.<br>\n\nThis renewed excitement shows that trance isn‚Äôt just a nostalgic throwback ‚Äî it‚Äôs evolving, merging underground sensibilities with mainstream festival energy, and 2025 is shaping up to be a landmark year for the genre.', 5, 7, 'http://13.60.95.22:3001/uploads/images/articles/optimized-article-1755247445670-366770454.jpg', NULL, 'image', 1, 0, 1, 'published', 'Trance Revival 2025, Euphoric Trance, 140 BPM Sets, Aly & Fila, Paul van Dyk, European Festivals, Electronic Music Trends, Dancefloor Hits', 'Trance Revival', 'Trance music surges across Europe with euphoric 140 BPM sets', 7, '2025-08-15 10:01:13', '2025-08-15 08:44:13', '2025-08-19 18:39:42'),
(17, 'Fred again.. & Skrillex Surprise B2B Set', 'Electronic music fans went wild as Fred again.. and Skrillex performed an unannounced B2B set in London, sending social media into a frenzy.', 'In one of the most talked-about moments of 2025, <strong>Fred again.. and Skrillex</strong> delivered a surprise B2B set at a London warehouse last weekend. The spontaneous performance, never announced in advance, brought together fans from across the UK and Europe, all eager to witness the unexpected collaboration.<br>\n\n<p>The set seamlessly fused Fred again..‚Äôs emotive, melodic house with Skrillex‚Äôs signature bass-heavy drops, creating a high-energy, genre-blending experience. Clips from the event quickly went viral on TikTok, X, and Instagram, with fans dubbing the moment ‚Äúthe unmissable set of the year.‚Äù</p>\n\n<p>Industry insiders suggest this could mark the beginning of a new wave of cross-genre collaborations, bridging melodic house, dubstep, and experimental electronic music. The performance also teased unreleased tracks from both artists, hinting at future joint releases that fans are already buzzing about.</p>', 5, 7, 'http://13.60.95.22:3001/uploads/images/articles/optimized-article-1755247908260-287564381.webp', NULL, 'image', 1, 0, 0, 'published', 'Fred again.., Skrillex, B2B Set, Viral Moment, London Warehouse, Electronic Music Collaboration, 2025 EDM, Melodic House, Dubstep, TikTok Trend', 'Fred & Skrillex', 'Fred again.. & Skrillex deliver surprise viral B2B set', 6, '2025-08-15 09:59:37', '2025-08-15 08:51:57', '2025-08-18 15:43:48'),
(18, 'üéß Calvin Harris Returns to Ibiza', 'Calvin Harris announces double residency at Ushua√Øa Ibiza for Summer 2025.', 'Scottish DJ and producer <strong>Calvin Harris</strong> is set to make a grand return to Ibiza this summer with a groundbreaking double residency at <strong>Ushua√Øa Ibiza.</strong> This marks the first time an artist has held two weekly residencies at the iconic venue in a single season, reflecting Harris\'s enduring popularity and influence in the electronic music scene.<br>\n\n<p>The residency will feature 25 exclusive shows, taking place every Tuesday and Friday starting August 26, 2025, and running through the end of the season. Harris is expected to showcase his signature blend of house, dance, and pop-infused tracks, alongside special guest performances and cutting-edge visuals.</p><br>\n\n<p>Fans can expect a high-energy atmosphere, with Harris bringing his chart-topping hits and new material to one of the world\'s most renowned open-air venues. Tickets are anticipated to sell out quickly, so early booking is recommended.</p>', 1, 7, 'http://13.60.95.22:3001/uploads/images/articles/optimized-article-1755250027044-115211847.webp', NULL, 'image', 1, 0, 0, 'published', 'Calvin Harris, Ushua√Øa Ibiza, Ibiza Residency 2025, Electronic Music, House Music, Dance Music, Ibiza Summer 2025, Live DJ Performances', 'üéß Calvin in Ibiza', 'Calvin Harris announces double residency at Ushua√Øa Ibiza', 19, '2025-08-15 10:23:34', '2025-08-15 09:03:44', '2025-08-19 11:47:17'),
(20, 'New Generation Of South American Talent Takeover!', 'Mochakk Brings Brazilian Heat to Hollywood Boulevard with All-Star Lineup', '<p><strong>The S√£o Paulo sensation teams up with Beatport chart-toppers Beltran and Maz for an unmissable street party in the heart of LA.</strong></p><p>Brazilian house phenomenon <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mochakk\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Mochakk</a> is set to shut down one of LA\'s most iconic thoroughfares this November, announcing a takeover of Hollywood Boulevard on <strong>15th November</strong> that promises to be his most ambitious US show yet.</p><p>The <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/hollywoodtakeover/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#HollywoodTakeover</a> will see the CircoLoco resident joined by two of Brazil\'s hottest electronic exports ‚Äî <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/beltranmusic\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Beltran</a> and <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mazmusic\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Maz</a> ‚Äî creating an all-Brazilian lineup that showcases the South American nation\'s explosive influence on global electronic music.</p><p>The event, produced by Framework in partnership with Mochakk, represents the promoter\'s fourth takeover of Hollywood Boulevard and will be Mochakk\'s largest West Coast performance to date, with capacity exceeding 10,000. Framework previously made history with Fisher and Chris Lake\'s 12,000-person <em>Under Construction</em> event in 2023 ‚Äî the first high-capacity event permitted on the street since 2000.</p><p><em>\"The Hollywood Boulevard is legendary ‚Äî to be able to perform there feels like a huge step, not just for my career but personally,\"</em> Mochakk tells RA. <em>\"My fans in the US have been incredible, and this moment feels like a celebration of all the hard work and passion that\'s brought me here.\"</em></p><h3>Rising Stars Unite</h3><p>The supporting cast reads like a who\'s who of Brazil\'s new generation of electronic music exports.</p><p>Beltran ‚Äî real name Juliano Beltran ‚Äî shot to prominence with his 2022 Beatport #1 hit <em>Smack Yo‚Äô</em> on Michael Bibi\'s Solid Grooves label, transforming from an IT security specialist moonlighting as a DJ into one of the scene\'s most sought-after names. The ga√∫cho from southern Brazil has since played CircoLoco at DC10 and Coachella, even befriending his idol Michael Bibi.</p><p>His catalog spans labels like Cuff and Revival New York, with releases earning support from heavyweights including Gordo, Marco Carola, Solardo, Pete Tong, and fellow Brazilians Vintage Culture and Mochakk himself.</p><p>Meanwhile, Maz has become one of contemporary Brazilian electronic music\'s most prominent names, reaching the top of Beatport charts five times, including a #1 Overall with <em>Amana</em>. His breakthrough came with a rework of <em>Banho de Folhas</em> by Luedji Luna, which became the best-selling Brazilian electronic music release on Beatport during 2022 and 2023, earning support from Black Coffee, Michael Bibi, Keinemusik, and Vintage Culture.</p><p>As founder of the Dawn Patrol label, Maz has been cultivating an artistic community focused on Afro House that incorporates elements of Brazilian percussion and culture. With 3.7 million monthly Spotify listeners, he\'s established himself as a key figure in exporting Brazilian electronic music globally.</p><h2><strong>Brazilian Wave Continues</strong></h2><p>The announcement caps off what\'s been a meteoric year for Pedro Maia, whose <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/mochakkcalling/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#MochakkCalling</a> events have been selling out across the globe.</p><p>From his residency at CircoLoco Ibiza to festival slots at Coachella, Glastonbury, and Cercle, the Brazilian producer has firmly established himself as one of electronic music\'s most exciting new voices. His US tour has already taken him from a Tricks &amp; Tracks skatepark pop-up at Venice Beach to sold-out shows in New York, Miami, and Chicago, but the Hollywood Boulevard event promises to be something entirely different.</p><p>Just two years ago, Mochakk was playing Framework\'s smaller Sound Nightclub venue; now he\'s headlining a 10,000+ capacity street party. Fresh off the release of his <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ninjatune\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Ninja Tune</a> EP <em>From The Stars</em> earlier this year, Mochakk is gearing up for his debut on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/disorderrecs\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Disorder Records</a> with <em>Legumes feat. KWENGFACE</em>, dropping this <strong>Friday 22nd August</strong>.</p><p>This weekend sees him headline <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/panoramafestival\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Panorama Festival</a> in Southern Italy alongside <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/peggygou_\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Peggy Gou</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/realblackcoffee\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Black Coffee</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/solomun\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Solomun</a>.</p><p>The all-Brazilian lineup underscores the country\'s growing influence on the global electronic scene, with artists like Vintage Culture, Classmatic, and ANNA leading a new wave of South American talent making waves internationally.</p><p>Pre-sale tickets for the Hollywood Boulevard takeover go live <strong>Friday 18th August at 10AM PT</strong>, with general sale following at 12PM PT the same day. Tickets are available through DICE and Framework\'s official channels.</p><p><em>Follow </em><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/residentadvisor\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>@ResidentAdvisor</em></a><em> for more electronic music news and </em><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mochakk\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>@Mochakk</em></a><em> for updates on the #BrazilianTakeover.</em></p><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/mochakk/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#Mochakk</a> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/hollywoodboulevard/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#HollywoodBoulevard</a> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/brazilianhouse/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">#BrazilianHouse</a></p>', 1, 7, 'http://13.60.95.22:3001/uploads/images/articles/optimized-article-1755255856951-968708327.webp', NULL, 'image', 0, 0, 0, 'published', '#HollywoodBoulevard#Beltran#gaucho#Maz', 'New Generation Of South American Talent Takeover!', 'The supporting cast reads like a who\'s who of Brazil\'s new generation of electronic music exports.', 32, '2025-08-15 11:15:00', '2025-08-15 11:15:58', '2025-08-19 17:50:43'),
(21, 'Mau P Drops Electrifying Single ‚ÄòTESLA‚Äô', 'Mau P‚Äôs new single ‚ÄòTESLA‚Äô is already making waves with its booming basslines, futuristic synths, and festival-ready energy. Early fan reactions and thousands of streams show it‚Äôs set to become a standout track in his 2025 tour and beyond.', '<p>Mau P continues to dominate the house music landscape with his latest single, ‚ÄòTESLA,‚Äô a pulsating track that blends booming basslines with futuristic synths.</p><p>Released yesterday, the track is already generating buzz for its festival-ready energy, perfect for mainstage moments. Mau P‚Äôs signature style‚Äîgritty, raw, and unrelenting‚Äîshines through, with early streams on Spotify and SoundCloud showing thousands of plays within hours.</p><p>Fans on X are calling it a ‚Äúgame-changer‚Äù for his upcoming sets at festivals like Tomorrowland Brasil. The track‚Äôs sleek production and driving rhythm make it a must-hear for house heads, with its infectious groove destined to ignite dancefloors worldwide.</p><p>Mau P teased the release on Instagram (@maupmusic), hinting at a music video dropping soon. As he gears up for a packed tour schedule, ‚ÄòTESLA‚Äô solidifies his place as one of 2025‚Äôs most exciting acts. Expect this one to climb the Beatport charts fast.</p>', 1, 7, NULL, 'https://soundcloud.com/realmaup/tesla', 'soundcloud', 0, 1, 0, 'published', '#MauP, #HouseMusic', 'Mau P Unleashes New Single ‚ÄòTESLA‚Äô ‚Äì A Festival Anthem', 'Mau P‚Äôs new track ‚ÄòTESLA‚Äô brings booming basslines, futuristic synths, and festival energy‚Äîalready trending on Spotify and SoundCloud.', 6, '2025-08-17 18:23:00', '2025-08-19 15:27:17', '2025-08-19 19:04:42'),
(22, 'KAYTRANADA Drops AIN‚ÄôT NO DAMN WAY! Ahead of Justice Tour', 'KAYTRANADA‚Äôs latest offering delivers infectious grooves and intricate beats that have fans and critics buzzing.', '<p>Canadian producer KAYTRANADA has set the scene ablaze with his new album, <em>AIN‚ÄôT NO DAMN WAY!</em>, released just in time for his co-headline tour with Justice, kicking off October 16. Known for his genre-blending mix of house, funk, and hip-hop, KAYTRANADA‚Äôs latest offering delivers infectious grooves and intricate beats that have fans and critics buzzing. Tracks like ‚ÄúHold On‚Äù and ‚ÄúDancefloor Dreams‚Äù are already dominating playlists, with their lush synths and irresistible rhythms. The album‚Äôs vibrant energy is a perfect precursor to the high-octane performances expected on tour, where KAYTRANADA‚Äôs signature live sets will merge seamlessly with Justice‚Äôs electro-heavy sound. Social media is flooded with clips of fans vibing to the new tracks, and Spotify playlists are showcasing the album‚Äôs lead singles. This release solidifies KAYTRANADA‚Äôs place as a trailblazer, pushing electronic music into bold, soulful territory.</p><ul><li>‚Äã<strong>Socials:</strong> @KAYTRANADA (Instagram, X/Twitter, Facebook)</li><li>‚Äã<strong>Hashtags:</strong> #KAYTRANADA #AintNoDamnWay #JusticeTour #ElectronicMusic #NewMusic</li></ul><p><br></p>', 5, 7, 'http://13.60.95.22:3001/uploads/images/articles/optimized-article-1755618953011-756528704.jpg', NULL, 'image', 0, 0, 0, 'published', '', '', '', 5, NULL, '2025-08-19 15:58:26', '2025-08-19 17:07:15'),
(23, 'Monolink‚Äôs ‚ÄòIn My Place‚Äô Previews New Album', 'Monolink‚Äôs latest single ‚ÄúIn My Place‚Äù offers a soulful preview of his upcoming album The Beauty Of It All, blending deep house with emotional lyricism. Already climbing on Spotify, the track showcases his signature fusion of organic and electronic sounds.', '<p>German producer Monolink dropped ‚ÄòIn My Place‚Äô on August 16, a soulful single from his upcoming album, <em>The Beauty Of It All.</em></p><p>Shared via EDM Cave, the track blends deep house with introspective lyrics, earning praise for its emotional depth. Monolink‚Äôs Instagram (@monolinkmusic) shared a live performance clip, showcasing his multi-instrumental talent.</p><p>Streams on Spotify are climbing, with fans on X calling it a ‚Äúmasterpiece.‚Äù The single sets the stage for Monolink‚Äôs European tour, with stops at major festivals.</p><p>This release highlights his ability to fuse organic and electronic sounds, making it a standout in 2025‚Äôs melodic house scene.</p>', 4, 7, NULL, 'https://open.spotify.com/track/2DtRDayrAhv5KnrIKFXgrs?si=66444605907f4036', 'spotify', 0, 1, 0, 'published', '#Monolink #DeepHouse', 'Monolink Drops Soulful Single ‚ÄòIn My Place‚Äô', 'Monolink‚Äôs new single ‚ÄòIn My Place‚Äô previews his upcoming album The Beauty Of It All, blending deep house with emotional lyrics and rising streams on Spotify.', 13, '2025-08-17 20:05:00', '2025-08-19 17:08:41', '2025-08-19 18:49:09'),
(24, '&FRIENDS‚Äô 12-Hour Halloween Rave in Manila', '&FRIENDS is hosting a 12-hour Halloween rave in Manila on October 31, 2025, headlined by Knock2. Fans can expect nonstop high-energy sets and exclusive visuals.', '<p>&amp;FRIENDS announced a 12-hour Halloween rave in Manila headlined by Knock2, set for late October 2025. The event, scheduled for <strong>October 31, 2025, at Okada Manila</strong>, will also feature artists like Dabin, BEAUZ, and SABAI, promising a nonstop high-energy experience (<a href=\"https://www.andfriends.live/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">tickets &amp; info</a>).</p><p>Shared via EDM House Network, the rave builds on &amp;FRIENDS‚Äô successful May event. Fans are already buzzing on social media, with Knock2 teasing exclusive visuals on Instagram (<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/reel/DM2RxYHBNC3/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Knock2 Instagram</a>) and Facebook (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/andfriends.fest/videos/friends-presents-manilas-biggest-halloween-rave-knock2-makes-his-long-awaited-ph/616283274880054/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Knock2 Facebook teaser</a>).</p><p>The rave highlights Manila‚Äôs growing EDM scene, with &amp;FRIENDS positioning itself as a key player in Asia‚Äôs festival circuit. While no official streaming links are available yet on platforms like Spotify, SoundCloud, Beatport, or YouTube, fans can stay updated with visuals and announcements via the festival‚Äôs official channels (<a href=\"https://edm.com/events/andfriends-festival-malta-lineup-2025/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">EDM.com event page</a>).</p><p>With Knock2‚Äôs bass-heavy sets expected to dominate the night, this marathon Halloween rave promises to be one of 2025‚Äôs standout EDM experiences in Asia.</p>', 2, 7, 'http://13.60.95.22:3001/uploads/images/articles/optimized-article-1755624097562-972473580.jpg', NULL, 'image', 0, 0, 0, 'published', '#FRIENDSFestival #Knock2 #ManilaRave #EDM2025 #HalloweenRave', '&FRIENDS Hosts 12-Hour Halloween Rave in Manila', '&FRIENDS‚Äô 12-hour Halloween rave in Manila features Knock2 and top DJs, promising nonstop EDM action and exclusive visuals on Oct 31, 2025.', 3, '2025-08-17 20:24:00', '2025-08-19 17:25:44', '2025-08-19 18:50:22'),
(25, 'James Hype‚Äôs ‚ÄòWaterfalls‚Äô Festival Anthem Released', 'James Hype drops his festival-ready tech house anthem ‚ÄòWaterfalls‚Äô, featuring infectious rhythms and massive drops. Already trending on Spotify, it‚Äôs set to dominate 2025 festival sets.', '<p>James Hype‚Äôs ‚ÄòWaterfalls‚Äô Festival Anthem Released James Hype unleashed ‚ÄòWaterfalls,‚Äô a festival-ready tech house anthem, on August 16. Shared via Edmtrain, the track‚Äôs infectious rhythm and massive drops are already dominating streams on Beatport. Hype‚Äôs Instagram (@jameshype) posted a clip of the track rocking H√Ø Ibiza, with fans on X hyping its mainstage potential. The single‚Äôs bold production and catchy vocal hooks make it a contender for 2025‚Äôs festival season. As Hype prepares for his SYNC shows, ‚ÄòWaterfalls‚Äô is set to become a staple in his high-energy sets, cementing his status as a tech house titan.</p>', 4, 7, NULL, 'https://open.spotify.com/track/1OcV53oesLQw3VTW9I3uD3?si=949b6695e5b346f1', 'spotify', 1, 0, 1, 'published', '#JamesHype, #Waterfalls, #TechHouse, #FestivalAnthem, #EDM2025', 'James Hype Releases Festival Anthem ‚ÄòWaterfalls‚Äô', 'James Hype‚Äôs new tech house single ‚ÄòWaterfalls‚Äô is a festival-ready hit with catchy hooks and massive drops, trending on Spotify for 2025 sets.', 3, '2025-08-16 20:48:00', '2025-08-19 17:50:24', '2025-08-19 18:53:48');
