(26, 'Cosmic Gate‚Äôs ‚ÄòNever Erase You‚Äô Single Drops', 'Cosmic Gate‚Äôs new single ‚ÄúNever Erase You‚Äù featuring Diana Miro blends emotive vocals with progressive trance, previewing their upcoming Perspectives EP 2. Released on August 16, the track is already resonating with fans and gaining traction on Spotify.', '<p>GRAMMY-nominated duo <strong>Cosmic Gate</strong> released <strong>‚ÄòNever Erase You‚Äô</strong> featuring Diana Miro, a preview of their upcoming <em>Perspectives EP 2</em>, on August 16, 2025. The track blends emotive vocals with progressive trance, already gaining traction on <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/1mJtIx9L9U9qvISv1yThEe\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Spotify</a> and <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LUZaoJ3tWlM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube</a>.</p><p>Shared via EDM Cave, fans are praising the single‚Äôs euphoric melodies, with X posts calling it a ‚Äúfestival banger.‚Äù Cosmic Gate‚Äôs Instagram (<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/cosmicgate\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">@cosmicgate</a>) shared a clip of their Parookaville set, teasing the track‚Äôs live debut.</p><p>The duo‚Äôs ability to craft emotionally charged anthems continues to captivate listeners worldwide, and ‚ÄòNever Erase You‚Äô is poised for chart success. As Cosmic Gate gears up for a global tour, this release reaffirms their influence in the trance music scene.</p><p><strong>Listen on Spotify:</strong> <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/1mJtIx9L9U9qvISv1yThEe\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Never Erase You ‚Äì Cosmic Gate ft. Diana Miro</a></p><p><strong>Watch on YouTube:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LUZaoJ3tWlM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Never Erase You Official Video</a></p>', 4, 7, NULL, 'https://open.spotify.com/track/1mJtIx9L9U9qvISv1yThEe?si=acd57310569142a0', 'spotify', 0, 0, 0, 'published', '#CosmicGate, #NeverEraseYou, #DianaMiro, #ProgressiveTrance, #EDM2025, #PerspectivesEP2', 'Cosmic Gate Drops \'Never Erase You\' with Diana Miro', 'Cosmic Gate\'s \'Never Erase You\' featuring Diana Miro blends emotive vocals with progressive trance, previewing their upcoming Perspectives EP 2.', 3, '2025-08-16 21:00:00', '2025-08-19 18:00:37', '2025-08-19 20:09:36'),
(27, 'Charlie Sparks‚Äô Techno Pop-Up at London Bakery', 'UK techno star Charlie Sparks hosted an unannounced pop-up at EK Bakery in Hackney, London, showcasing unreleased tracks and electrifying a passionate crowd. Clips from the event are going viral on TikTok.', '<p>UK techno star <strong>Charlie Sparks</strong> took over <strong>EK Bakery</strong> in Hackney, London, for an unannounced pop-up event on August 16, 2025, celebrating his latest release. The event, dubbed <strong>‚ÄúBack From The Baker‚Äù</strong>, transformed the bakery into a high-energy rave, featuring Sparks\' signature hard techno sound. From 6:30 to 8:30 PM, fans packed the intimate space, surrounded by industrial ovens and the aroma of fresh bread, creating a unique and immersive experience.(<a href=\"https://mixmagde.com/read/charlie-sparks-brings-techno-chaos-to-an-east-london-bakery-for-back-from-the-baker-pop-up-news?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Mixmag Germany</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ravejungle.com/2025/08/12/charlie-sparks-back-from-the-baker-pop-up/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Rave Jungle</a>)</p><p>The pop-up event was shared via <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/charliesparksmusic/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Charlie Sparks\' Instagram</a> and <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ekbakery/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">EK Bakery\'s Instagram</a>, showcasing clips of the night. Additionally, fan-made videos from the event have been circulating on <a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@charliesparksmusic/video/7529473053194079510\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">TikTok</a>, amplifying its viral reach.(<a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/%40charliesparksmusic/video/7529473053194079510?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">TikTok</a>)</p><p>This unconventional venue choice highlights techno\'s ability to transform spaces, with fans praising Sparks\' chaotic energy and the event\'s DIY spirit. As Sparks prepares for upcoming tour dates in the US, Lisbon, Malta, Germany, and Ibiza, this pop-up signals a growing trend of spontaneous, community-driven techno events.(<a href=\"https://mixmagde.com/read/charlie-sparks-brings-techno-chaos-to-an-east-london-bakery-for-back-from-the-baker-pop-up-news?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Mixmag Germany</a>)</p><p><strong>Listen to \"Back From The Baker\" on SoundCloud:</strong></p><p> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/charlie-sparks-531540495/back-from-the-baker\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Back From The Baker ‚Äì Charlie Sparks</a></p><p><strong>Watch the official teaser on TikTok:</strong></p><p> <a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@charliesparksmusic/video/7529473053194079510\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Back From The Baker Teaser ‚Äì Charlie Sparks</a></p><p><strong>Follow Charlie Sparks on Instagram:</strong></p><p> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/charliesparksmusic/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Charlie Sparks Instagram</a></p><p><strong>Follow EK Bakery on Instagram:</strong></p><p> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ekbakery/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">EK Bakery Instagram</a></p><p><br></p>', 5, 7, 'http://13.60.95.22:3001/uploads/images/articles/optimized-article-1755627133903-822663915.jpeg', NULL, 'image', 0, 0, 0, 'published', '#CharlieSparks, #TechnoPopUp, #LondonEvents, #EDM2025, #BackFromTheBaker', 'Charlie Sparks‚Äô Techno Pop-Up Hits EK Bakery London', 'Charlie Sparks surprises fans with a techno pop-up at EK Bakery, London, performing unreleased tracks and creating viral TikTok buzz on Aug 16, 2025.', 1, '2025-08-16 21:14:00', '2025-08-19 18:17:51', '2025-08-19 19:04:53'),
(28, 'Lollapalooza 2025 Lineup Brings Diverse EDM Talent', 'Lollapalooza 2025 in Chicago showcases a diverse EDM lineup featuring Zedd, REZZ, and Gryffin, with high-energy sets across progressive house, bass music, and more.', '<p>Lollapalooza 2025\'s electronic music lineup, announced on March 18, is one of its most diverse yet, featuring heavyweights like <strong>Zedd</strong>, <strong>REZZ</strong>, and <strong>Gryffin</strong>. The Chicago festival, scheduled for July 31 to August 3 at Grant Park, promises high-energy performances across genres, from progressive house to bass music. (<a href=\"https://pitchfork.com/news/lollapalooza-2025-lineup-announced-tyler-the-creator-sabrina-carpenter-asap-rocky?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Pitchfork</a>)</p><p>The announcement has sparked a frenzy on X (formerly Twitter), with fans hyping sets at Grant Park. The festival\'s Instagram (@lollapalooza) posted a vibrant lineup graphic, driving ticket sales. (<a href=\"https://www.lollapalooza.com/lineup?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">lollapalooza.com</a>)</p><p>This year‚Äôs focus on electronic music reflects the genre‚Äôs growing dominance, with organizers curating a blend of established and rising acts. As excitement builds, Lollapalooza continues to solidify its status as a must-attend event for EDM fans. Tickets are selling fast, so grab yours now.</p><p><strong>Listen to EDM Highlights from Lollapalooza 2025:</strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZeddLucky\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Zedd ‚Äì \"Lucky\" ft. Remi Wolf</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=REZZFallingLive\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">REZZ ‚Äì \"Falling\" (Live at Breakaway Festival)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GryffinLastOfUs\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Gryffin ‚Äì \"Last of Us\" ft. Rita Ora</a></li></ul><p><strong>Follow Lollapalooza on Social Media:</strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lollapalooza\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a></li><li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/lollapalooza\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lollapalooza\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a></li></ul><p><strong>Tickets and More Information:</strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.lollapalooza.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Official Lollapalooza Website</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.ticketmaster.com/lollapalooza-tickets/artist/123456\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Ticketmaster ‚Äì Lollapalooza 2025</a></li></ul><p><br></p>', 2, 7, 'http://13.60.95.22:3001/uploads/images/articles/optimized-article-1755628145412-730222521.png', NULL, 'image', 0, 0, 0, 'published', '#Lollapalooza2025, #EDM, #Zedd, #REZZ, #Gryffin, #FestivalSeason, #ChicagoEvents', 'Lollapalooza 2025 EDM Lineup Revealed', 'Lollapalooza 2025 features Zedd, REZZ, and Gryffin with diverse EDM sets at Grant Park, Chicago. Tickets selling fast for this must-attend festival.', 0, '2025-08-17 21:26:00', '2025-08-19 18:29:12', '2025-08-19 18:29:12'),
(29, 'Pinkque & That Girl‚Äôs ‚ÄòBreathe Fire‚Äô Gets Artena Remix', 'Artena drops a high-octane remix of Pinkque & That Girl‚Äôs trance anthem ‚ÄúBreathe Fire‚Äù, enhancing its euphoric melodies with festival-ready driving beats. Already trending on Spotify, it‚Äôs a must-hear for trance fans in 2025.', '<p>On August 1, 2025, UK-based producer <strong>Artena</strong> released his high-octane remix of <strong>Pinkque &amp; That Girl‚Äôs</strong> trance anthem <strong>‚ÄúBreathe Fire‚Äù</strong>, available on <a href=\"https://www.beatport.com/release/breathe-fire-artena-remix/5183469\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Beatport</a>. The remix amplifies the original‚Äôs euphoric melodies with driving beats, making it a perfect fit for festival stages. Artena‚Äôs take has already garnered thousands of streams on <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/3sewygD5OxqrWyZuAJNdwj\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Spotify</a>, with trance fans on X praising its uplifting energy.(<a href=\"https://change-underground.com/pinkque-adds-to-her-discography-with-artenas-remix-of-breathe-fire/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Change Underground</a>, <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/3sewygD5OxqrWyZuAJNdwj?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Spotify</a>)</p><p>Pinkque‚Äôs <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/pinkquemusic\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> shared a teaser of the remix, sparking excitement for its inclusion in upcoming sets at events like Dreamstate SoCal. The track‚Äôs soaring synths and emotive vocals resonate with trance purists while appealing to new listeners.</p><p>This release underscores the genre‚Äôs enduring appeal, with Artena‚Äôs production elevating the track to new heights.</p><p><strong>Listen to the Remix:</strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eVCNt-Ecwdk\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blan